data.description: 4 bed/ 2.5 bed quick fixer with Master on Main. Home has been vacant for a while but systems are mostly in good condition. Needs updated landscaping, cosmetic updates, and the electrical panel may have a circuit issue. Great opportunity for a cash investor but also could pass financing guidelines for an owner occupant willing to do a little work. NOTE: Principals of the seller may share ownership in a licensed real estate brokerage.
